data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Exquisite townhouse nestled within Hidden Oaks subdivision, this remarkable end unit welcomes you the moment you approach the front door. Surrounded by lush greenery and overlooking a picturesque pond, the property offers a blend of natural beauty.    Step through the front entryway into a spacious living space, seamlessly transitioning into a dining area and a beautiful kitchen. The kitchen has ample storage, abundant cupboards, and expansive counter space, great for meal preparations. The refrigerator and dishwasher is brand new as of September 2023. The laundry room and large pantry is located off the kitchen. Adjacent to the dining area, discover a screened-in lanai that opens to a private backyard, an inviting space to unwind.    On the second story is a large master suite, with a generous walk-in closet and a master bathroom featuring double sinks, a soaking tub, and a spacious shower. Two additional generously sized bedrooms with spacious closets share access to another large full bathroom.  This townhouse is impeccable upkeep, this home emanates a sense of care and attention to detail. Don't miss the chance to own this stunning home —schedule your viewing today!
